    <item>
      <title>林吉特接近 26 年低点，你梦想的马来西亚假期变得更便宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/your-dream-malaysia-vacation-just-got-cheaper-with-ringgit-near-26-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从喧嚣的吉隆坡，到跳岛游，再到观赏大象，由于令吉疲软提振了游客的消费能力，马来西亚的各种景点现在增加了吸引力。该货币兑美元汇率最近短暂跌破 4.8——上一次达到这一水平是在 26 年前的亚洲金融危机期间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/your-dream-malaysia-vacation-just-got-cheaper-with-ringgit-near-26-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
